/uploads/getty_images/1178728033/image_1178728033.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Gearstd</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Is ZIM Integrated A Buy After The Ex-Dividend Date?</h2> <p><span>We previously covered </span><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4724982-zim-integrated-double-tailwinds-trigger-robust-near-term-dividend-prospects\">ZIM Integrated Shipping</a><span> (NYSE:</span><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ZIM\" title=\"ZIM Integrated Shipping Services Ltd.\">ZIM</a></span><span>) in October 2024, discussing why we had upgraded the stock to</span><span> a speculative buy for dividend oriented investors, thanks to</span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1178728033/image_1178728033.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742869-is-zim-integrated-a-buy-after-the-ex-dividend-date", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 17:30:00"}, {"id": "4742847", "title": "Brookfield Renewable Partners: One Of My Highest Conviction Investments", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200457452/image_200457452.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"USA, Arkansas, Beaver Lake Dam, elevated view\" data-id=\"200457452-001\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200457452/image_200457452.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200457452/image_200457452.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/200457452/image_200457452.jpg?