/article/4742872-adobe-heading-into-q4-two-key-ingredients-are-missing", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 17:00:55"}, {"id": "4742890", "title": "Okta: On The Path To A Rebound, Keep Holding On For Upside", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169876053/image_1169876053.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"OKTA headquarters in SOMA district, San Francisco\" data-id=\"1169876053\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6138px\" height=\"4094px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169876053/image_1169876053.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169876053/image_1169876053.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169876053/image_1169876053.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169876053/image_1169876053.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169876053/image_1169876053.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169876053/image_1169876053.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169876053/image_1169876053.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169876053/image_1169876053.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Sundry Photography</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Good value is hard to find in today\u2019s markets, and many investors, including myself are growing increasingly jittery on sky-high valuations. For that reason, investing in \u201cgrowth at a reasonable price,\u201d especially in stocks that haven\u2019t yet ridden a big momentum bump this</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1169876053/image_1169876053.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742890-okta-on-the-path-to-a-rebound-keep-holding-on-for-upside", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 16:31:18"}, {"id": "4742845", "title": "Constellation Brands: Reflecting Both The Weakness And Potential In Beverages", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1904538649/image_1904538649.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Hands of man and women toasting beer at music festival\" data-id=\"1904538649\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1904538649/image_1904538649.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1904538649/image_1904538649.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1904538649/image_1904538649.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1904538649/image_1904538649.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1904538649/image_1904538649.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1904538649/image_1904538649.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1904538649/image_1904538649.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1904538649/image_1904538649.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Klaus Vedfelt</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Dear readers/followers,</p> <p>One of my primary investments for the past year has been investment into the beverage and alcohol sector. This has been the case with companies such as Diageo (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DEO\" title=\"Diageo plc\">DEO</a>) and giants like LVMH (</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1904538649/image_1904538649.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742845-constellation-brands-reflecting-weakness-and-potential-in-beverages", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 16:30:00"}, {"id": "4742887", "title": "STAG Industrial: Use The Pullback To Your Advantage", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"phrase buy the dip handwritten on night wet window glass surface\" data-id=\"1289941019\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5472px\" height=\"3648px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-